        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Employee Retention Tax Credit Reinstatement Act</strong></p> <p>This bill provides for a reinstatement of the employee retention tax credit through 2021. The credit was established to compensate employers whose businesses were negatively impacted by the COVID-19 pandemic for wages paid to their employees.</p>]]>
        </text>
